{"tid":1307453,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"啲蝗原來可以無限次來港！！","createTime":"2019-07-11T14:44:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T10:15:41.000Z","uid":127479,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7378e13fa3a7fb5d2a49707abb5bd0eddb320819","tid":1307453,"uid":127479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T14:44:10.000Z","msg":"暗訪片段：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/715486135226112/posts/2660027260771980?s=524433800&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F715486135226112%2Fposts%2F2660027260771980%3Fs%3D524433800%26v%3De%26sfns%3Dmo&d=mly3UyGsD7RWnvW57yDWjrZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=a798365a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/715486135226112/posts/2660027260771980?s=524433800&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n民主黨立法會議員林卓廷表示，接獲前線入境處人員反映，不少內地居民手持個人遊簽注來港，用完後可以無限次續簽，變相可以無限制來港。<br />\n<br />\n政府發言人晚上回覆查詢時表示，內地居民赴港簽注屬內地職權範圍，只要符合要求和規定便可申請，每次申請相隔時間沒有限制。特區政府會繼續留意內地居民赴港情況，與內地當局保持溝通。<br />\n<br />\n根據政府提供數據顯示，自2015年4月，內地當局停止向深圳戶籍居民簽發「一簽多行」個人遊簽注，改發「一周一行」，內地持個人遊簽注入境本港人次，在2015年按年下跌近340萬人次，數字至2017年一直下跌至逾2500萬人次。不過數字在去年已回復至與2014年水平相約，近3130萬人次。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌唔撚怪之得咁多蝗嚟不斷污染香港<br />\n不過有度好，可以方便我哋輸出革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家唔好俾佢停<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13385d7e1f8106d04ca596ad9b5adbe66d601241","tid":1307453,"uid":5499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T14:47:07.000Z","msg":"唔怪得咁撚迫"},{"pid":"d0575fa8e585d065712ee3ec6e615ea373978b47","tid":1307453,"uid":139474,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T14:47:14.000Z","msg":"[集結!]民陣7月21日金鐘集會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1307426\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1307426</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"90d6a24051cc08e20b1d20437b27cd7d8482084b","tid":1307453,"uid":127479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T14:56:26.000Z","msg":"屌你老母<br />\n個個落嚟做雞做公安<br />\n一吹雞要去打義士拆牆就半夜都仆到過嚟<br />\n用哂大陸嗰套乸渣招，打人打到盡，人民鬥人民<br />\n我哋要攞返我哋嘅香港啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e85cd1bc4a4933eb717967b7646a0ebcad2da5e1","tid":1307453,"uid":127479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T15:51:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5d5d99bcba56e433246085a904914ec01320334","tid":1307453,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T15:51:56.000Z","msg":"無限我哋輸出革命"},{"pid":"e371096b2aca7b5622720d82b5de66660c855b32","tid":1307453,"uid":127479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T10:15:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}